prompts.frontCover:
Flat 2D illustration for a greeting card front cover, in a charming and loose watercolor style with soft edges and beautiful color bleeding.

The scene is a humorous and chaotic kitchen. An illustrated cartoon version of Lao Lao from the photo, wearing her light blue sweatshirt, stands proudly next to a wobbly, comically leaning, multi-layered birthday cake that looks like it might topple over at any moment. She's holding a spatula covered in frosting and has a mischievous, triumphant grin with a little smudge of frosting on her cheek. An illustrated cartoon version of Jordan from the photo, wearing his tan hoodie, peeks out from behind a doorway, his eyes wide with a mix of awe and playful fear as he looks at the cake creation.

The kitchen is whimsically messy, with splatters of watercolor frosting on the counter, a few scattered sprinkles on the floor, and a rolling pin left askew. The background is simple, with soft pastel watercolor washes in shades of mint green and butter yellow to make the characters and cake pop.

Floating in the center of the card, in an elegant, readable, hand-written cursive script in a dark teal color, is the text: "Happy Birthday Lao Lao".
